WEBVTT

00:00:06.965 --> 00:00:10.455
In the sun-dappled streets 
of a small town,

00:00:10.455 --> 00:00:14.400
a proud mother 
showed off her newborn son.

00:00:14.400 --> 00:00:16.588
Upon noticing his lucky birthmark,

00:00:16.588 --> 00:00:20.380
townsfolk predicted 
he would marry a princess.

00:00:20.380 --> 00:00:24.600
But soon, these rumors reached the ears 
of the wicked king.

00:00:24.600 --> 00:00:30.121
Enraged, the king stole the child away, 
and sent him hurtling down the river.